  <span id="freeText17615786605869150529" style="display:none"><br /><b>Change.Org Petition: Despicable Munroe</b><br /><br />The International Astronomical Union recently named an asteroid after Randall Munroe; asteroid <i>4942 Munroe</i> is big enough to cause a mass extinction if it ever hits Earth.<br /><br />Not that he needs an asteroid to do that. He has his minions devising millions of ways to do it, on a subversive site they call <a href="http://www.xkcd.com" rel="nofollow noopener">xkcd.com</a>. This book is a set of leaked manuals. <br /><br />It should be clear to all how dangerous this guy (and his site) really is. But all Government agencies fail to heed my warnings. <br /><br />I exhort you to read this and then contact your local representative immediately. We can stop him. Together. <br /><br />If you still have doubts, let me remind you of numerous disaster movies — there is always only ONE GUY who saw it coming! Do you really want to ignore me?<br /><br />Eager for your support,<br /><br />Thanks.</span>
