<span id="freeTextContainer3809778751668105563">This is a lot of fun from a guy who likes when things catch fire. <br/><br/>A lot of the questions reminded me of the ones Neil Gaiman fielded after Geoff Coffey&apos;s tweet that he would donate $1 to @EFF for every person who asks @neilhimself how they can watch American Gods in their country.</span>
  <span id="freeText3809778751668105563" style="display:none">This is a lot of fun from a guy who likes when things catch fire. <br /><br />A lot of the questions reminded me of the ones Neil Gaiman fielded after Geoff Coffey's tweet that he would donate $1 to @EFF for every person who asks @neilhimself how they can watch American Gods in their country.</span>
