        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3493275261" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7239935958661846204"><strong>A fun, absurd, and informative book that I couldn&apos;t out down!</strong><br/><br/>What If? Serious Scientific Answers to Absurd Hypothetical Questions by Randall Munroe is a fun book! Crazy questions are answered but answered scientifically! He also puts in a section called Weird and Worrisome Questions which have some really strange questions and then shows a cartoon of him as if he was first reading it! Hilarious! Lots of his cartoons are sprinkled throughout the book! This book is funny but informative too. I had</span>
  <span id="freeText7239935958661846204" style="display:none"><strong>A fun, absurd, and informative book that I couldn't out down!</strong><br /><br />What If? Serious Scientific Answers to Absurd Hypothetical Questions by Randall Munroe is a fun book! Crazy questions are answered but answered scientifically! He also puts in a section called Weird and Worrisome Questions which have some really strange questions and then shows a cartoon of him as if he was first reading it! Hilarious! Lots of his cartoons are sprinkled throughout the book! This book is funny but informative too. I had fun reading this and learned a few things besides the fact that some of my fellow earthlings are very strange indeed! 😁</span>
  <a data-text-id="7239935958661846204" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


